@startuml
title 3.1 整体流程业务时序图
hide footbox
autonumber

actor "用户端" as User
participant "版权服务" as Service
participant "MySQL" as DB
participant "MinIO" as OSS
participant "审核端" as Reviewer
participant "链上合约" as Chain

User -> Service: 提交文件与元数据
activate Service

Service -> DB: 查询 fileHash 是否已存在
DB --> Service: 查询结果
Service -> DB: 查询 normalizedHash 是否已存在
DB --> Service: 查询结果

Service -> OSS: 上传原始文件
OSS --> Service: 返回 fileStorageId
Service -> DB: 写入 application/evidence

Service -> DB: 加载最近200条 semanticHash 候选
DB --> Service: 返回候选样本
Service -> Service: 计算 maxScore 与 sameSubject

alt 需要人工复核
  Service -> DB: 更新 application.status=PENDING_REVIEW
  Service --> User: 返回申请受理（待人工复核）
  Reviewer -> Service: 提交复核结论

  alt 复核驳回
    Service -> DB: 更新 application.status=REJECTED
    Service --> Reviewer: 返回复核完成（驳回）
  else 复核通过
    Service -> Chain: registerEvidence(rootHash, metadataHash)
    Chain --> Service: txHash, blockNumber
    Service -> DB: 写入版权记录并更新 ONCHAIN_SUCCESS
    Service --> Reviewer: 返回复核完成（上链成功）
  end

else 自动通过
  Service -> Chain: registerEvidence(rootHash, metadataHash)
  Chain --> Service: txHash, blockNumber
  Service -> DB: 写入版权记录并更新 ONCHAIN_SUCCESS
  Service --> User: 返回上链成功
end

deactivate Service
@enduml